{"ts":"2026-07-15T20:00:17.934Z","author":"codex-audit-20260715","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"Live reproduction on pm 2026.7.15: pm plan create --help --json exits 2 with unknown_command and says the plan create path is not exposed. The same runtime documents create in the positional subcommand argument of pm plan --help while returning subcommands as an empty array. This violates the repository rule that agents should inspect exact runtime help before mutation. Fix the model coherently: either register real nested subcommands or teach help, contracts, and completion that positional plan actions are command paths. Preserve all plan features and aliases."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-2tan"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Plan positional-action help is undiscoverable: pm plan create --help is rejected as an unknown command"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Make the documented plan action grammar self-describing so agents can inspect exact create and step flags without falling into generic unknown-command recovery."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","area:cli","contracts","help","plan"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-15T20:00:17.934Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-15T20:00:17.934Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-audit-20260715"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":120},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"pm plan create --help and --help --json resolve to action-specific help or an equally precise positional-action help view; pm help plan create and command-scoped contracts expose the same effective flags; shell completion advertises plan actions; pm plan --help no longer reports an empty subcommands array while describing subcommands only in a positional argument; documented pm plan create examples remain valid; regression tests cover help JSON, contracts, completion, and unknown-command recovery"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-15T20:00:17.934Z","author":"codex-audit-20260715","text":"Duplicate check evidence: all-status searches for plan create help unknown command positional action contracts found only broad roadmap and historical audit entries with no focused active or terminal owner."}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"f02a46a097b1a1d345c866d1f2e43548f6f216802793a4283b0fe1bdd963a905","message":""}
